           <h1 class="title">Khatabook app - manage your expenses </h1>
           <h2 class="overview"> 🚀 Overview</h2>
           <p class="project-intro">
           KhataBook App is a smart expense and ledger management system that allows users to add and manage their khatas and expenses in two ways — one that is always accessible and another that is password-protected for enhanced privacy. Only authorized users can view password-protected khatas. Users can easily update, delete, and manage their expenses, and even share them with others through WhatsApp or text messages. This app ensures both flexibility and security, making expense tracking simple, private, and shareable when needed.
           </p>

           <h2 class="feature">🔥 Features</h2>

          <ul>
            <li>📒 <span class="heading">Smart Khata Management</span> – Users can add and manage their khatas and expenses easily.</li>
            <li>🔐 <span class="heading">Password-Protected Khatas</span> – Only authorized users can view private khatas.</li>
            <li>🌐 <span class="heading">Public & Private Modes</span> – Users can choose between always-accessible or secure khatas.</li>
            <li>✏️ <span class="heading">Edit & Delete Options</span> – Easily update or remove any expense entry.</li>
            <li>📤 <span class="heading">Expense Sharing</span> – Share expense details via WhatsApp or text message.</li>
            <li>📆 <span class="heading">Organized Tracking</span> – Maintain a clean and categorized record of all expenses.</li>
          </ul>


           <h2 class="techstack">🛠️ Tech Stack</h2>

           <ul>
              <li><span class="heading">Frontend :</span> EJS, CSS, JS</li>
              <li><span class="heading">Backend:</span> Node.js, Express.js</li>
              <li><span class="heading">Database: </span> MongoDB (Atlas) </li>
              <li><span class="heading">Authentication: </span> JWT</li>
           </ul>
           
           <h2 class="how-work">🎮 How It Works</h2>

          <ol>
            <li><span class="heading">Add a Khata – </span>Users can create a new khata by entering details like title, amount, and type (public or password-protected).</li>
            <li><span class="heading">Choose Privacy Mode – </span>Select between public (always accessible) or private (password-protected) khata types.</li>
            <li><span class="heading">Add Expenses –</span>Users can add detailed expense entries under each khata.</li>
            <li><span class="heading">Edit or Delete –</span>Users can modify or remove any expense they have added.</li>
            <li><span class="heading">Share Khata –</span>Khata or expense details can be shared via WhatsApp or text message directly from the app.</li>
          </ol>


